Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.00,0:01:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第三十话\N复仇的恶鬼\N志志雄真正的谋略
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.68,0:01:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你往哪逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.96,0:02:04.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你以为这样 我就杀不了你了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.64,0:02:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种手刺突剑法 出奇不意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.51,0:02:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能让敌人无法招架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:26.15,0:02:28.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是新撰组副队长 土方岁三
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.68,0:02:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所发明的剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.99,0:02:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而我的牙突剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:34.22,0:02:35.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比他更厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.49,0:02:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是牙突剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.17,0:02:52.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,自以为是的家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.61,0:02:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是我从十年前到现在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.85,0:02:59.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,经过无数次危难
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.15,0:03:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所练出来的剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:00.92,0:03:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你能如何招架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.79,0:03:06.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个人好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.52,0:03:09.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.93,0:03:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.37,0:03:21.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,让开
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.21,0:03:33.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然绯村胸部已受伤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.15,0:03:36.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他第二次的反击\N会比第一次快速
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.32,0:03:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我猜的没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.95,0:03:42.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙\N已慢慢燃起决斗的战火
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.99,0:03:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不过还未完全恢复从前的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.30,0:03:48.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.50,0:03:50.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.64,0:04:04.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比我预期的还要快
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:07.68,0:04:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心的呼吸愈来愈快了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.17,0:04:36.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果他全力以赴 和我决斗的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.01,0:04:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就得使出 真正的牙突剑法了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.02,0:04:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在才是真正的牙突剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.21,0:05:09.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 牙突剑这么简单就被打挎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.01,0:05:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤 你在京都和我决战时\N用的就是这一招
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.45,0:05:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到过了十年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.26,0:05:29.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一点长进也没有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.36,0:05:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在这一招对我 已完全没有作用了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.00,0:05:35.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起来 我们的决斗还没结束
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.10,0:05:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,决斗 我现在不想和你决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.61,0:05:43.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.71,0:05:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这句话该是我说才对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.32,0:05:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.39,0:05:56.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心 又变回过去的他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.86,0:06:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,进来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.43,0:06:06.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,阻止他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.68,0:06:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再这样下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:30.53,0:06:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心会消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.54,0:07:18.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下一次是你的人头 落地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.54,0:07:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手 谁来阻止他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.74,0:07:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小薰 别费神了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.35,0:07:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,左之助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.68,0:07:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们无法阻止他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.42,0:07:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心现在已回到从前的他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.19,0:07:36.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在幕府的京都中战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.69,0:07:39.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他听不到我们的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.50,0:07:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有决一死战
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.33,0:07:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,分出胜负 他们才会停手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.38,0:07:55.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,川路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.88,0:07:57.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.04,0:08:01.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤进入道场多久了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.55,0:08:05.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,已四个小时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.02,0:08:10.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们快去阻止他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.06,0:08:12.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚了就来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.43,0:08:13.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.37,0:08:20.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,刀折断了还能用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.70,0:08:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,又是牙突剑法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:22.04,0:08:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是新撰组的成员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:25.61,0:08:30.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新撰组家规第一条\N士可杀不可辱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.55,0:08:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不允许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:33.35,0:08:35.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,临阵脱逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.02,0:08:36.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没武器了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.92,0:08:39.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这下剑心赢定了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.25,0:08:42.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,死到临头还嘴硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.59,0:08:49.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙还想赤手抵挡剑心\N看他有多大能耐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.53,0:08:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,制服的皮带
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:59.37,0:09:00.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:00.24,0:09:01.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,糟了 没有剑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.91,0:09:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心胜算就不大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:06.25,0:09:08.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我让你死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:08.72,0:09:12.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心会被勒死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:13.22,0:09:15.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想勒断剑心的脖子\N没那么容易
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:15.62,0:09:18.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是武士的决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:31.91,0:09:34.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是幕府式的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.01,0:09:39.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,二人都在做最后的一击
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:39.98,0:09:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论生死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:42.45,0:09:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,都要拼个你死我活
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就快分出胜负了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.03,0:09:54.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也该结束了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.70,0:09:56.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.63,0:10:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤 住手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.33,0:10:32.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别忘了你的任务\N只是测知绯村剑心的实力而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.47,0:10:37.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 既然警察督长这么说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就到此为止了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,警察督长
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.94,0:10:42.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,测知实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.38,0:10:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是怎么一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:45.01,0:10:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤 我知道你武功高强
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我想你也不愿意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.59,0:10:55.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看绯村剑心就此白白牺牲吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.89,0:11:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来 真正的幕后指使者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.30,0:11:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是你这个萨摩藩维新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.66,0:11:08.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明治政府内务省长\N大久保利道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:12.27,0:11:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保利道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.71,0:11:19.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这些人究竟在讲什么\N我怎么一句也听不懂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.45,0:11:22.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小鬼不懂少废话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.25,0:11:23.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,咦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:23.18,0:11:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明治维新的三位领导人 西乡隆盛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,桂小五郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:30.39,0:11:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以及目前仅存的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.13,0:11:35.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是这位大久保先生吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.73,0:11:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在则是日本最高大臣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.17,0:11:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我没想到会造成今天的局面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.61,0:11:50.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但我真正的目的\N只是想测知你们的实力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.88,0:11:53.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为我有不得已的苦衷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.58,0:11:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不快说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.69,0:11:58.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.72,0:12:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来就是这个超级大人物\N大久保
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.52,0:12:05.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快回去向涉海老大禀告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:11.50,0:12:15.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正下次有的是机会\N我再找你决斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.64,0:12:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算你命大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.34,0:12:19.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.14,0:12:22.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 斋藤
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:22.38,0:12:23.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,斋藤向你报告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.64,0:12:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村剑心只不过是个\N虚有其表的窝囊废罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.91,0:12:30.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无法胜任大任 以上报告完毕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.05,0:12:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙虽是警察厅的密探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.62,0:12:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但却让人捉摸不定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.99,0:12:43.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村 外头备有马车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.33,0:12:44.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.50,0:12:46.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有话现在直说就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.03,0:12:51.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想知道整件事的不只是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.92,0:13:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在场的每一个都有权利知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.42,0:13:09.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在场的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.16,0:13:11.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有话就快说吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.86,0:13:15.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心又恢复清醒了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.07,0:13:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.17,0:13:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么啊 大笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.97,0:13:24.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,祢彦 还不快去拿药箱来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.47,0:13:25.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:25.21,0:13:28.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心你别这样\N大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.14,0:13:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:29.81,0:13:32.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在我们也只能\N顺从他的意思了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.38,0:13:40.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就直说吧 绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.65,0:13:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄现正在京都为非作乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:45.09,0:13:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保先生 谁又是志志雄了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.96,0:13:51.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你少插嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.17,0:13:56.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄和我一样\N都是武士出身的杀手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:56.30,0:13:59.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,志志雄属于长州派的维新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.04,0:14:04.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,和我不同的是\N他专搞地下活动从不出面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.21,0:14:07.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此大家就称他\N影子杀手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.82,0:14:10.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当时大家也都认为\N他是我的继承者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.35,0:14:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.92,0:14:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,继承者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.45,0:14:15.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有这回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:15.59,0:14:17.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此包括我在内
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.63,0:14:23.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,几乎没人见过\N他的庐山真面目
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.50,0:14:29.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,传说志志雄在十年前\N戊辰战争中战死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.24,0:14:35.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但其实\N他是被同志给杀死的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.08,0:14:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这是为确保国家安全
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:42.12,0:14:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不得已采取的手段
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.82,0:14:51.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然 志志雄的武功和你不相上下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.99,0:14:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他却是一个名利薰心的危险人物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:59.17,0:15:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由于维新志士们非常了解 志志雄的实力与价值
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.81,0:15:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以暗杀的计划无法公开\N否则必会造成日本的大混乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.38,0:15:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但如果不除掉他 日本就会被其操控
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.89,0:15:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩弄于股掌间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.69,0:15:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.66,0:15:25.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们就趁着戊辰战争时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:25.46,0:15:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,将他杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.39,0:15:31.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,本想放火烧死他
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.37,0:15:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没想到他虽然全身烧灼 却死里逃生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.31,0:15:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从那时候起 志志雄就化为复仇魔鬼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:46.08,0:15:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成为喜好战斗 破坏和平的武器商人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.15,0:15:53.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在其领导下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.99,0:15:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在京都的黑街内 组成一支庞大的地下兵团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.99,0:16:00.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,颠复日本 分化这个国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.53,0:16:05.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是他的复仇计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:05.83,0:16:10.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们好几次派出平反的军队\N却全被他打败
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.77,0:16:13.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在只有靠你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.54,0:16:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绯村
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.61,0:16:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了国家与人民\N你一定要回京都一趟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:20.05,0:16:22.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这么说来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.55,0:16:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就是要剑心 去刺杀志志雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.03,0:16:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.53,0:16:37.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,当然 我们会付出庞大的报酬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.16,0:16:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且对你们过去的违法行为 也既往不究
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:47.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比方说 我们不会抓小惠小姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.14,0:16:53.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开什么玩笑\N你们休想拿我来威胁剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:53.18,0:16:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,否则我宁愿去死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.68,0:17:03.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们这群卑鄙的小人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.06,0:17:06.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们休想拿虚伪的理由 逼剑心就范
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:06.16,0:17:09.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心既然决定不再杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.66,0:17:11.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,现在也不会再为你们杀人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:11.67,0:17:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你给我闭嘴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.37,0:17:15.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这关系到国家存亡的危机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无能的政府
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:20.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还不都是你们这群人造成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.17,0:17:23.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,政府的繁荣\N人民的和平就看这次了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.91,0:17:26.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是你们家的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:26.08,0:17:28.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再胡说我就逮捕你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.28,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,试试看呀 你这狗官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:30.15,0:17:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然我不知道你们在吵什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.75,0:17:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要杀志志雄是你们的事 别来找剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.56,0:17:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们可别一意孤行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.13,0:17:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:44.40,0:17:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你们需要剑心的帮助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:48.64,0:17:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但他现在已决定\N收手不再杀人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.24,0:17:55.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们也绝不让他到京都去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.78,0:17:56.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:56.48,0:17:57.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,绝不让他去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.85,0:18:00.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑心是我们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:00.35,0:18:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们会守着剑心的\N无论发生什么事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.38,0:18:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:04.82,0:18:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,国家的命运 就要毁于你们手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.89,0:18:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 川路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:08.36,0:18:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.06,0:18:17.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你们可以再考虑看看 不必急着回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.31,0:18:27.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保利通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.44,0:18:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.38,0:18:33.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原来 斋藤是大久保的走狗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:33.95,0:18:38.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 只要我揭发这个秘密
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.42,0:18:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就可以做下任的内务卿了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.12,0:18:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别开玩笑了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.82,0:18:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保是何等的超级大人物\N我还想保住我的小命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:47.29,0:18:53.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你就别再拖我下水\N让我到上海去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.94,0:18:58.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看你上海也别去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.54,0:19:01.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,地狱更适合你去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.42,0:19:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涉海 你还是一点都没变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.25,0:19:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你表面假装是维新志士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.46,0:19:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,骨子里却在完成自己的私欲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.43,0:19:24.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是有你这种败类 国家才会大乱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.53,0:19:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的工作就是为政府做密探
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.63,0:19:31.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,专门找出像你这种该杀的败类
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:31.47,0:19:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这就是新撰组的使命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.78,0:19:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:36.88,0:19:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有害国家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.28,0:19:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就要除恶务尽 绝不饶赦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.89,0:19:47.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下 我可以给你钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:47.82,0:19:51.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,狗有饲料就行 人可以用钱买通
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.46,0:19:57.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是却买不到正义的大野狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:58.00,0:20:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,过去是 现在也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.60,0:20:04.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,新撰组就是新撰组
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:04.64,0:20:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大野狼就是大野狼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.34,0:20:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剑客就是剑客
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.58,0:20:12.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧 绯村剑心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.96,0:20:35.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一星期后的五月十四日 我会再来找你们的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:35.74,0:20:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就等五月十四日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:39.74,0:20:45.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大久保先生 你比十年前消瘦了不少
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.95,0:20:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为了国家的前途 这是应该的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.89,0:21:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我会等你们的好消息的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:12.94,0:21:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这一夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.07,0:21:17.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们见到大久保大人的最后一夜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:17.14,0:21:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明治十一年五月十四日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.62,0:21:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我们人生的转折点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.58,0:21:29.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,它将改变我们每个人的命运
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:29.26,0:21:31.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但现在谁也不知道究竟会如何
